reviewText: my kids used to enjoy watching them when they were younger so I thought I would get it for my grandkids to see if they liked them
It's Chip 'n Dale: Rescue Rangers. The boxes are well made and if you grew up watching Disney Afternoons, you know this was one of their best shows.
this was a gift and they loved it :)

Arrived when promised
No problems with DVD

Got this for my daughter for Christmas and it's her favorite gift! The quality was not good, clearly not digitally enhanced, but she loves it more for this reason. It's the original, the way she remembers it!
